00:33:41,660 --> 00:33:43,100
Didn’t you read the note

580
00:33:43,140 --> 00:33:44,220
on last page of the contract?

581
00:33:44,220 --> 00:33:45,940
What note?

582
00:33:46,340 --> 00:33:49,140
If you break the contract, you’ll need to pay double penalty!

583
00:33:49,140 --> 00:33:50,140
What?

584
00:34:02,700 --> 00:34:03,180
You…

585
00:34:51,100 --> 00:34:51,980
The fragrance from

586
00:34:51,980 --> 00:34:53,900
blackberry and raspberry.

587
00:34:54,540 --> 00:34:56,800
Together with the fresh smell of meadow.

588
00:34:57,420 --> 00:34:58,260
Aftertaste

589
00:34:58,780 --> 00:35:01,310
