596
00:35:59,940 --> 00:36:01,180
All ruined!

597
00:36:11,780 --> 00:36:12,380
Mr. Lu.

598
00:36:12,540 --> 00:36:13,180
How is it?

599
00:36:14,660 --> 00:36:16,780
Empty the barrels of

600
00:36:17,340 --> 00:36:18,220
product No. 92.

601
00:36:18,420 --> 00:36:19,620
All of them?

602
00:36:20,260 --> 00:36:21,820
Yes. All Brett.

603
00:36:22,060 --> 00:36:22,580
Well,

604
00:36:22,740 --> 00:36:24,860
if it’s all Brett…

605
00:36:44,580 --> 00:36:45,220
Well…

606
00:36:46,020 --> 00:36:48,460
Where did you get the barrels?

607
00:36:49,260 --> 00:36:50,380
I thought you said…

608
00:36:53,180 --> 00:36:56,310
The winemaker said that he wanted some used oak barrels,

609
00:36:56,620 --> 00:36:58,660
in order to reduce the effect of the barrel on the wine.

610
00:36:58,660 --> 00:37:01,220
So, these barrels were bought from Gaoling Winery.

611
00:37:01,220 --> 00:37:02,420
What about cleaning?

612
00:37:02,620 --> 00:37:04,860
They were cleaned once before delivered here.

613
00:37:04,860 --> 00:37:06,140
The pomace

614
00:37:06,260 --> 00:37:08,140
in the barrels No. 92 and 93

615
00:37:08,300 --> 00:37:09,900
had slight acetic smell,

616
00:37:10,140 --> 00:37:11,820
so we just left it there

617
00:37:11,900 --> 00:37:13,630
and used the barrels directly.

618
00:37:15,060 --> 00:37:16,420
Empty the barrels.

619
00:37:17,140 --> 00:37:19,100
Then take them to the outside,

620
00:37:19,420 --> 00:37:22,180
and sterilize them with high concentration alcohol.

621
00:37:22,180 --> 00:37:23,180
Get it done today.

622
00:37:23,500 --> 00:37:23,980
Okay.

623
00:37:24,140 --> 00:37:26,260
It’s such a waste to throw them all!

624
00:37:31,700 --> 00:37:32,380
Mr. Ma.

625
00:37:33,300 --> 00:37:36,140
What is that Bre…

626
00:37:36,300 --> 00:37:37,660
What were you talking about?

627
00:37:37,660 --> 00:37:39,500
It’s Brett.

628
00:37:40,100 --> 00:37:42,060
It smells a little bit like animal.

629
00:37:42,540 --> 00:37:45,060
You can imagine the smell of stable.

630
00:37:46,060 --> 00:37:47,260
Small amount of Brett

631
