638
00:38:18,540 --> 00:38:20,980
So you are really going to dump all the wine?

639
00:38:24,860 --> 00:38:26,340
The wine is all turned.

640
00:38:27,020 --> 00:38:27,980
It’s not wine!

641
00:38:29,620 --> 00:38:31,620
But dumping it all is too far.

642
00:38:32,260 --> 00:38:34,580
Even though it doesn’t taste good,

643
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:36,640
it’s not poisonous after all.

644
00:38:36,980 --> 00:38:38,220
It takes a lot of manpower, material and financial resources

645
00:38:38,220 --> 00:38:40,260
to make wine.

646
00:38:40,740 --> 00:38:42,780
