647
00:38:42,940 --> 00:38:45,380
Wine is a gift of nature.

648
00:38:46,020 --> 00:38:47,940
The flavor of the wine can be simple,

649
00:38:47,940 --> 00:38:49,400
but cannot be unpleasant.

650
00:38:50,020 --> 00:38:51,750
If we sell the unqualified wine

651
00:38:52,140 --> 00:38:53,670
just for saving some money,

652
00:38:54,940 --> 00:38:57,540
it’ll be a disrespect to the work of

653
00:38:58,100 --> 00:38:59,940
sunshine, climate and yeast.

654
00:39:12,860 --> 00:39:14,340
Getting rid of the unqualified

655
00:39:14,340 --> 00:39:16,140
is a respect to the qualified.

656
00:39:18,020 --> 00:39:20,620
Although this Lu Weixun is quite annoying,

657
00:39:20,980 --> 00:39:24,580
