661
00:40:14,420 --> 00:40:15,500
Magic water?

662
00:40:19,180 --> 00:40:20,580
Yes, magic water!

663
00:40:21,380 --> 00:40:23,340
I hope you can introduce our magic water

664
00:40:23,340 --> 00:40:26,500
